      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has started to soften, add the <strong>meat-free mince</strong> to the pan</p><p>Cook for 3-4 min, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong></p>",
