      "instruction": "<p>Add 350ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[700ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>halved green beans</strong> and <strong>sultanas</strong></p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until the water is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
